<figureCitation id="13252A1EB4696F2E6C78FE86FD05FED9" box="[527,645,319,345]" captionStart="FIGURES 21 ­ 32" captionStartId="15.[264,382,1463,1487]" captionTargetBox="[278,1287,310,1403]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[265,1321,308,1456]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 21 ­ 32. Female genitalia. Figs. 21 ­ 23, 29. Apterodina bechynei; 21, ovipositor, ventral view; 22, dorsal hood of segment IX. 23, segment VIII, dorsal view; 29, spermatheca. Figs. 24, 32, Apterodina ruminyahui; 24, ovipositor, ventral view; 32, spermatheca. Figs. 25 ­ 27. 30, Brachypterodina morae; 25, ovipositor, ventral view; 26, dorsal hood of segment IX. 27, segment VIII, dorsal view; 30 (above and right), spermatheca; 28 (left and below), Brachypterodina gonzalezi, spermatheca. 31, Apterodina bucki, spermatheca." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/157659/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">21–23, 29</figureCitation>
